E4Plus1.uk.description: The Separation Agitation: Howard and Bernadette are upset when they leave Halley at the nursery. Bert the geologist introduces his girlfriend to the gang. (S10 Ep21/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cognition Regeneration: Leonard isn't happy when he finds out that Penny is considering accepting a job offer from her ex-boyfriend Zack. (S10 Ep22/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gyroscopic Collapse: Amy is offered a fellowship at Princeton, Raj makes new living arrangements, and the guys' gyroscope project spins out of control. (S10 Ep23/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Long Distance Dissonance: The gang worry when Sheldon's former admirer, Dr Ramona Nowitzki, turns up while Amy is away working at Princeton. (S10 Ep24/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Kid Who Would Be King
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Fantasy adventure. A 12-year-old from modern-day suburbia finds King Arthur's sword Excalibur and must save the country from a sinister sorceress. With Patrick Stewart.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great New Year Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: Noel, Matt, Prue and Paul get festive with bakers of Bake Off past Helena, Henry, Nancy and Rahul, who compete to become festive star baker. And there's a cosy sing-song around the piano.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons: Wiggum's Way
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Love Lisa: Lisa gives Ralph Wiggum a card on Valentine's Day. But when he falls in love with her, it leads to a bitter feud between their families. (S4 Ep15/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons: Wiggum's Way
E4Plus1.uk.description: New Kids on the Blecch: Ralph and Bart are recruited by a top record producer to be part of a new boy band. (S12 Ep14/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons: Wiggum's Way
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Simpsons Spin-Off Showcase: Chief Wiggum becomes a hard-boiled private investigator, in a vision of the future hosted by Troy McClure. (S8 Ep24/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons: Wiggum's Way
E4Plus1.uk.description: Uncut Femmes: There's more to Sarah Wiggum than anyone suspected, as Marge learns when she gets involved in a jewel heist. (S32 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons: Wiggum's Way
E4Plus1.uk.description: How the Test Was Won: Ralph is swept away on a rubbish barge during a journey to Capital City. Homer desperately avoids danger after failing to renew his insurance. (S20 Ep11/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Keanu Reeves returns for the third time as the supposedly retired hitman. Someone's put a contract on John Wick's head and only a mystic in Morocco can lift it.

GBNews.uk.title: Patrick Christys Tonight
GBNews.uk.description: Join Patrick for two hours of spirited debate and news making interviews. Top guests tackle the issues that matter, with a sharp take on every story.

GBNews.uk.title: Patrick Christys Tonight Late Edition
GBNews.uk.description: Tomorrow's news, tonight. All the major stories making the front pages and full coverage of all the breaking news at home and abroad with Patrick Christys.

GBNews.uk.title: The Late Show Live
GBNews.uk.description: Live from Washington DC, Bev Turner and Ben Leo bring you the latest from the US and what it means for Britain.

GBNews.uk.title: Farage
GBNews.uk.description: Nigel Farage doesn't hold back in his GB News prime-time show. Hear his views and give your own in an hour of discussion and debate. Join Nigel as he takes on the big stories other media won't touch.

GBNews.uk.title: Patrick Christys Tonight
GBNews.uk.description: Join Patrick for two hours of spirited debate and news making interviews. Top guests tackle the issues that matter, with a sharp take on every story.

GBNews.uk.title: Patrick Christys Tonight Late...
GBNews.uk.description: Edition. Tomorrow's news, tonight. All the major stories making the front pages and full coverage of all the breaking news at home and abroad with Patrick Christys.

GBNews.uk.title: Breakfast with Stephen and Ellie
GBNews.uk.description: Join Stephen Dixon and Ellie Costello to start your day across the United Kingdom. This is your breakfast show. Join the conversation about what is happening in our nation and the world.

GBNews.uk.title: Britain's Newsroom
